    "title": "ひとつ、ふたつ、夢に誘われ",
    "enTitle": "",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ここのところ根を詰めていたせいか――\n作業が一段落しても、上手く眠れない日々が続いている……。",
            "enText": "I wonder if it's because I've been working too hard lately but―― \nEven after finishing all my work, I haven't been able to sleep well……",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ふああぁぁ～……",
                    "enText": "Fuwaaah～……",
                    "nextBlock": 2
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4980431267860737583,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ちょっと、はしたないわよ！　にしても……まだ寝不足なの？\nわたしが作ったソープやバスボムも効かなかったみたいね……。",
            "enText": "Hey, that's really unbecoming of you! That said…… \nAre you still not getting much sleep? Looks like \nthe soap and bath bombs I prepared didn't work……",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 381,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "リラックスはいい案だと思ったんだけど……",
                    "enText": "I thought it was a good idea though……",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 159,
                    "pathId": -8326864832450031172
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3844029755883607004
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6643201204692831940,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "うーん……もっと別のアプローチがいいのかしら？",
            "enText": "Yeah……Maybe we should try a different approach?",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 139,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 164,
                    "pathId": 5100721423211636387
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 177,
                    "pathId": 446973989198345330
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -252083613246616469,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "いつまでもこんなことじゃ、そのうち倒れちゃうわ。\n他にもいろいろ試してみましょう！",
            "enText": "If we don't do something, you'll collapse eventually. \nLet's try a few other things!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 201,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": 9085470322271052438
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -6376546361321997379
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6926133543654704876,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はい――次は、疲れをリセットするストレッチ。仰向けに寝転んで、\n体を弓なりにカーブ――そう、上体を伸ばすことを意識して。",
            "enText": "Okay――Next, some stretches while resetting fatigue. Lie \ndown on your back and then bend your body like it's a bow―― \nJust like that, focus on stretching your upper body.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 362,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "くっ……！結構きつい……！",
                    "enText": "Kuu……! This is kinda hard……!",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": -550253571969487133
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": -7948938880393128005
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 232,
                    "pathId": -75457457181829435
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 367637218528780057,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ストレッチの後は、ヨガで自律神経を整えましょう。\n寝転んで、合蹠のポーズから。",
            "enText": "After stretching, let's try some Yoga to create a sense \nof balance in the autonomic nervous system. Lie down, \nand we'll start with some poses for joint health.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 298,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 2016417076123287148
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -9208131076110022180
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 328,
                    "pathId": 3599825911820260514
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5491893216120629960,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "胡坐をかくみたいにひざを曲げて、足の裏同士を合わせて――",
            "enText": "Bend your knees, move as if you're going to sit \ncross-legged but place the soles of your feet together――",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 177,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "わ、わかった……っ！",
                    "enText": "G-got it……!",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 320,
                    "pathId": 644732947872841681
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": 4620084304007891529
                },
