        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "やるって決めたら、必ずやり遂げるんだから！\n貴方をぐっすり眠らせるまで、諦めないわよ……！",
            "enText": "Since I've already decided, then I need to do it! \nUntil you're sound asleep, I won't give up……!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 239,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
