            "pathId": 6954753241641580263,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "そういうことだから。\n――羊を数えるわよ、わたしが！",
            "enText": "And that's why―― \nWe'll start counting sheep, or at least I will!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 146,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "そ、それって効くのか！？",
                    "enText": "I-is that how it works!?",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "そ、それって効くの！？",
                    "enText": "I-is that how it works!?",
                    "nextBlock": 15
