        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "一応根拠はあるのよ？　一定のリズムは脳に安心感を与えるし、\n同じことが繰り返される話を聞いていると、眠くなるの。",
            "enText": "There is some basis for it though? A steady rhythm \ncan give the brain a sense of security, and repeatedly \nhearing the same words can make you sleepy.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 318,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "animData": [
